# Production Deployment Checklist

**Purpose**: Pre-submission verification steps. Apply before building for App Store submission.

## Pre-Submission Checklist
- Set `forceOnboarding = false`
- Set `forceShowPaywall = false`
- Remove hardcoded API keys (use Config.plist)
- Wrap debug prints in `#if DEBUG` where appropriate
- Verify Info.plist keys are set (privacy descriptions, encryption)

## Build Configuration
- Build with Release configuration
- Verify code signing is correct
- Increment build number for new submissions
